Is the European elite ready to do business with Britain?
The Business for Britain campaign was launched in April with the promise of bringing together businesses and defining what wealth and job creators want to see change in our relationship with the EU.
To do this, we ordered the largest and most comprehensive survey from British business leaders and asked them what they thought about Britain, companies and the EU.
YouGov has interviewed more than 1,000 business leaders, globally representative of all sizes of businesses, sectors and regions in Britain.
